          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "A new method for determining integral partial cross",
                " sections of photonuclear reactions in (gamma,xgamma')",
                " experiments was applied to studying partial channels",
                " of Na-23 GDR decay. Integral partial cross sections",
                " obtained for 20 deg decay channels which have been",
                " observed before. Contributions were found introduced",
                " by semidirect processes to the mechanisms of Na-23",
                " dipole photoabsorption."
              ]
            }
          ],
